01:01:27,050 --> 01:01:30,210
你还记得我一直说的那棵树吗
And you know that tree I'm always going on about?

523
01:01:30,210 --> 01:01:31,670
记得
Yeah.

524
01:01:31,870 --> 01:01:35,530
这药是拿那种树做的
Well, this drug is made from trees like that.

525
01:01:35,600 --> 01:01:37,020
- 是吗 - 没错
- It is? - Yeah.

526
01:01:37,190 --> 01:01:38,550
真的?
Seriously?

527
01:01:38,750 --> 01:01:41,900
一直以来 我们本能出去砍掉它
All this time we could have gone out there and just chopped it down.

528
01:01:43,280 --> 01:01:44,940
但那一棵不行
But not that one.

529
01:01:49,260 --> 01:01:51,480
那一棵是我们的朋友
That one's our friend.

530
01:02:29,600 --> 01:02:31,250
你在哪
Where are you?

531
01:02:32,260 --> 01:02:33,620
我在这
I'm here.

532
01:02:36,040 --> 01:02:38,800
你能让我妈妈好转吗
Can you do it? Can you make my mum better?

533
01:02:38,810 --> 01:02:41,970
你母亲能被治愈的话 紫杉树会那么做
If your mother can be healed, the yew tree will do it.

534
01:02:44,810 --> 01:02:49,140
- 所以是可以咯? - 你还是不知道你为什么召唤我
- So that's a yes? - You still don't know why you called me.

535
01:02:49,140 --> 01:02:52,890
我没有召唤你 就算有也是为了我妈妈
I didn't call you. And even if I did, it was obviously for mum.

536
01:02:52,890 --> 01:02:54,360
- 是吗 - 还能怎么样
- Was it? - What else?

537
01:02:54,370 --> 01:02:56,870
那些蠢故事毫无意义
To listen to idiotic stories that make no sense.

538
01:02:56,880 --> 01:03:01,930
现在还不是讲第三个故事的时候 但快了 在那之后
It is not yet time for the third tale. But soon. And after that...

539
01:03:01,930 --> 01:03:04,730
你要告诉我你的故事 康纳・奥马利
you will tell me your story, Conor O'Malley.

540
01:03:04,730 --> 01:03:07,170
不
No.

541
01:03:07,340 --> 01:03:10,510
不 不是这个 这只是一场噩梦
No, not this. That's just a nightmare.

542
01:03:10,680 --> 01:03:13,140
别这样
No, please.

543
01:03:16,340 --> 01:03:19,690
那不是真的 那不过是一场噩梦
That's not my truth. That's just a nightmare.

544
01:03:19,860 --> 01:03:23,030
然而这会在第三个故事之后发生
Nevertheless, this will happen after the third tale.

545
01:03:23,200 --> 01:03:25,400
我想知道我妈妈会怎么样
I want to know what's going to happen with my mum.

546
01:03:26,430 --> 01:03:29,350
别浪费你被给予的宝贵时间
Do not waste the precious time that is given you.

547
01:03:29,350 --> 01:03:32,340
等等 你要去哪
Wait. Where are you going?

548
01:03:32,500 --> 01:03:35,140
如果你是治愈之树 那我需要你去救治
If you are a tree of healing, then I need you to heal.

549
01:03:37,010 --> 01:03:39,220
我会的
And so I shall.

550
01:04:09,360 --> 01:04:14,610
康纳 我会回来的 我保证 你来洛杉矶过圣诞
Conor, I'll come back. I promise, alright. And you'll come to LA for Christmas.

551
01:04:14,680 --> 01:04:17,180
我不想圣诞就留妈妈一个人
I wont leave mum alone for Christmas.

552
01:04:17,240 --> 01:04:20,620
- 康纳你妈妈用的这个药... - 会让她好转
- Conor this medicine your mum's taking... - Is going to make her well.

553
01:04:20,630 --> 01:04:22,680
康纳 很可能不会
No, Conor, it probably isn't.

554
01:04:22,680 --> 01:04:24,880
- 会的 - 这是最后一博了 儿子
- Yes it is. - No, it's a last stage effort, son.

555
01:04:25,040 --> 01:04:27,460
会治愈她的 我知道的
It will heal her. I know it.

556
01:04:28,490 --> 01:04:30,740
这就是它来的原因 一定是的
It is the reason it came. It has to be.

557
01:04:30,740 --> 01:04:33,490
- 什么来的原因 - 怪物
- Reason what came? - The monster.

558
01:04:33,490 --> 01:04:35,580
- 康纳  什么  - 它总会12点07分出现
- Conor, what? - It comes to 12h07.

559
01:04:35,590 --> 01:04:38,130
起初我以为这是一个梦 但它不是
At first I thought it was a dream, but there is always...

560
01:04:38,300 --> 01:04:39,860
康纳 别说了 那是个梦
Stop. It is a dream.

561
01:04:40,030 --> 01:04:42,350
只是个梦 我很抱歉你得面对这件事
That's all it is. I'm sorry you have to face this...

562
01:04:42,400 --> 01:04:44,670
但你得勇敢起来
but you have to be brave.

563
01:04:45,370 --> 01:04:48,120
明白吗
Do you understand?

564
01:04:49,060 --> 01:04:50,760
来吧
Come on.

565
01:04:51,780 --> 01:04:53,180
来吧
Come on.

566
01:05:03,450 --> 01:05:05,570
我会尽快回来
I'll be back as soon as I can.

567
01:05:06,020 --> 01:05:08,670
如果不够快怎么办
What if it's not fast enough?

568
01:05:14,160 --> 01:05:15,250
康纳 听着
Conor, listen...

569
01:05:15,420 --> 01:05:18,720
- 没事的 - 什么没事的
- It's okay. - What is okay?

570
01:05:18,880 --> 01:05:20,340
只是...
Just...

571
01:05:20,340 --> 01:05:22,530
你不用尽快
You don't have to.

572
01:06:30,640 --> 01:06:33,230
看到没
Look. Do you see it?

573
01:06:33,390 --> 01:06:35,230
看到了吗 你能挥手吗
Do you see it? Can you wave?

574
01:06:35,390 --> 01:06:38,240
你能看到他吗
Can you see him?

575
01:06:38,400 --> 01:06:42,830
向外婆挥手
And then we wave to grandma.

576
01:06:46,250 --> 01:06:48,080
嗨 外婆
Hello grandma.

577
01:06:48,250 --> 01:06:50,500
康 向外婆和妈妈打招呼
Con, you can say hello to grandma and mum?

578
01:06:50,670 --> 01:06:52,840
嗨 外婆
Hello Grandma.

579
01:06:53,010 --> 01:06:55,260
这就对了
Here we go.

580
01:06:55,430 --> 01:06:58,270
妈妈已经听过这个很多次了
Mum has heard this many times.

581
01:06:58,330 --> 01:07:00,170
你准备好了吗
Are you ready?

582
01:07:00,330 --> 01:07:02,510
康 过来
Con, come sit here.

583
01:07:02,670 --> 01:07:05,340
康 看啊
Con, look.

584
01:07:05,510 --> 01:07:08,180
- 你好 外婆  - 妈妈...
- Hello grandma. - Mama...

585
01:07:08,350 --> 01:07:10,350
妈妈
- one... - Mama.

586
01:07:10,520 --> 01:07:12,800
很好
There we go.

587
01:07:12,800 --> 01:07:15,440
外婆 我们在画画
We are doing your picture, grandma.

588
01:07:15,610 --> 01:07:18,450
然后混在一起
And then mix it together.

589
01:07:18,620 --> 01:07:20,120
这是什么颜色
What color is that?

590
01:07:20,690 --> 01:07:22,020
棕色
Brown.

591
01:07:24,630 --> 01:07:26,460
- 好看又幸运的棕色 - 棕色
- It is a nice lodgy brown. - Brown.

592
01:07:26,630 --> 01:07:29,470
- 但这里有棕色了 - 没错
- But we have brown here. - That's true.

593
01:07:29,630 --> 01:07:32,930
看到了吗
What can you see?

594
01:07:33,100 --> 01:07:36,100
那是什么 它们是什么
What is that? What are those?

595
01:07:36,270 --> 01:07:38,270
你觉得这些是什么
What do you... What are these?

596
01:07:38,440 --> 01:07:41,490
- 眼睛 - 眼睛 没错
- Eyes. - Eyes. That's it.

597
01:07:41,650 --> 01:07:44,240
生活永远都在眼睛之中
Life is always in the eyes.

598
01:07:44,760 --> 01:07:47,330
如果你懂的话
If you get that...

599
01:07:47,330 --> 01:07:49,910
你会是个出色的艺术家
you will be a proper artist.

600
01:07:50,360 --> 01:07:52,240
很好
Yes.

601
01:07:52,630 --> 01:07:55,380
看啊
Look.

602
01:07:55,550 --> 01:07:57,390
就是这么画眼睛
This is how we draw the eyes in...

603
01:07:57,560 --> 01:08:01,630
这里是眼睛捕捉映像的地方
because this is where the eyes catch the reflection.

604
01:08:02,690 --> 01:08:06,530
在眼睛里 我们能看到生活 看见没
There we see the life in the eyes. See that?

605
01:08:06,690 --> 01:08:11,410
再来一次 这就是生活
Do it again. It's life.

606
01:08:14,410 --> 01:08:17,840
用铅笔吧
Maybe if we take a pencil...

607
01:08:18,000 --> 01:08:21,680
然后在那里画
and you can draw on that...

608
01:08:21,840 --> 01:08:24,100
想试试吗
Do you want to try it?

609
01:08:24,260 --> 01:08:26,480
让我看看
Show me how you do it.

610
01:08:38,750 --> 01:08:42,340
看 康
Look, Con.

611
01:08:42,500 --> 01:08:47,510
那是他的头发 这是他的眉毛
That's his hair and this is his eyebrow.

612
01:08:48,970 --> 01:08:51,640
这边是眼睛
There's the eyes.

613
01:08:51,810 --> 01:08:54,560
看 这是他的嘴
Oh look, there's his mouth.

614
01:08:54,730 --> 01:08:58,400
这是他的嘴 他非得愤怒
There's his mouth. He is very angry.

615
01:08:58,570 --> 01:09:00,740
看到了吗
Can you see?

616
01:09:00,910 --> 01:09:03,490
看啊
Look at that.

617
01:09:04,060 --> 01:09:08,280
然后我们画张脸
And then we start to make a face.

618
01:09:08,280 --> 01:09:10,340
然后
And then...

619
01:09:10,500 --> 01:09:12,760
这就是我们的怪物
there's our monster.

620
01:09:12,920 --> 01:09:14,510
这就是怪物
There's the monster.

621
01:09:14,680 --> 01:09:17,270
看这怪物
Look at the monster.

622
01:09:51,690 --> 01:09:53,700
慢点
Very slowly.

623
01:09:55,280 --> 01:09:57,290
就是这样
That's it.

624
01:10:00,960 --> 01:10:03,210
没错 好的
That's it, okay.

625
01:10:14,280 --> 01:10:16,740
今早是30分钟的考试
Okay, so 30 minutes exam this morning...

626
01:10:16,900 --> 01:10:20,740
考的过去两周我们都做过的东西
and this is all the stuff we've been doing for the last two weeks.

627
01:10:20,910 --> 01:10:25,380
复习过就不会有意外
So if you've done your revision, there will be no surprises.

628
01:10:29,920 --> 01:10:33,190
你们马上就得合上书本
So in a moment I'm going to ask you to turn your pages over.

629
01:10:33,190 --> 01:10:39,270
下面30分钟都不准说话 要保持完全安静
There will be no talking for the next 30 minutes. I want total silence...

630
01:10:39,270 --> 01:10:43,570
因为你们要用的是大脑而不是嘴
because you are going to use your brains, not your mouths.

631
01:10:43,740 --> 01:10:45,990
30分钟...
So 30 minutes...

632
01:10:46,160 --> 01:10:48,830
现在开始 祝你们好运
Starting now. Good luck.

633
01:11:15,570 --> 01:11:19,030
在这么久之后
I think I've finally figures you out.

634
01:11:19,100 --> 01:11:21,600
我想我总算搞懂你了
After all this time.

635
01:11:21,770 --> 01:11:26,190
你只是想让人对你印象深刻
All you're looking for is someone kick your head in.

636
01:11:26,360 --> 01:11:27,860
但你知道吗
But you know what?

637
01:11:28,030 --> 01:11:31,030
我不再是那个家伙了
I'm not that guy anymore.

638
01:11:37,100 --> 01:11:39,220
再见 奥马利
Goodbye, O'Malley.

639
01:11:39,250 --> 01:11:42,010
我再也不会看见你
I no longer see you.

640
01:11:42,170 --> 01:11:45,340
现在你对我来说是隐形的
Now you're invisible to me too.

641
01:11:46,300 --> 01:11:48,700
希望你妈妈会好起来
I hope your mum gets better.

642
01:12:13,450 --> 01:12:15,480
你怎么这么慢
What took you so long?

643
01:12:15,480 --> 01:12:18,800
是时候讲第三个故事了
It's time for the third tale.

644
01:12:21,600 --> 01:12:24,930
曾经有个隐形人
There was once an invisible man...

645
01:12:24,930 --> 01:12:28,110
厌倦了不被人看见
who was grown tired of being unseen.

646
01:12:28,280 --> 01:12:32,080
实际上 他不是隐形的
It was not that he was actually invisible.

647
01:12:33,870 --> 01:12:37,540
只是人们习惯于无视他
It was just the people had become used to not seeing him.

648
01:12:37,710 --> 01:12:42,550
有一天 隐形人再也受不了了
One day, the invisible man couldn't stand it anymore.

649
01:12:42,710 --> 01:12:47,470
他好奇如果没人看见你
He kept wondering, if no one sees you...

650
01:12:47,640 --> 01:12:51,140
那你真的存在吗
Are you really there at all?

651
01:12:51,310 --> 01:12:54,150
隐形人做了什么
What did the invisible man do?

652
01:12:54,670 --> 01:12:58,750
他召唤了怪物
He called for a monster.

653
01:13:16,800 --> 01:13:19,910
我都不知道跟你说什么好 奥马利
I don't even know what to say to you, O'Malley.

654
01:13:21,180 --> 01:13:25,020
你把他送进了医院
You sent him to hospital.

655
01:13:25,190 --> 01:13:27,940
他父母威胁要起诉
His parents are threatening to sue.

656
01:13:28,110 --> 01:13:31,160
- 那不是我 - 什么
- It wasn't me. - What was that?

657
01:13:31,160 --> 01:13:33,620
那不是我
Wasn't me.

658
01:13:36,620 --> 01:13:40,090
我不是隐形的
I'm not invisible. I'm not invisible.

659
01:13:40,150 --> 01:13:42,900
如果你想被人注意 奥马利 那可不是最好的办法
If you want to be seen, O'Malley, this is not the best way.

660
01:13:42,900 --> 01:13:47,640
我不是隐形的 你听见了吗
I'm not invisible. Did you hear me? I'm not invisible.

661
01:13:47,800 --> 01:13:52,490
根据学校规定 你会被立即开除
School rules dictate immediately exclusion.

662
01:13:54,060 --> 01:13:58,900
但我是一名教师 我怎么可能做得到
But how could I do that and consider myself any kind of a teacher?

663
01:13:59,900 --> 01:14:01,620
回去上课吧
Go back to class.

664
01:14:01,620 --> 01:14:05,950
我们改日再谈 今天就不谈了
We will talk about this one day, but not today.

665
01:14:06,490 --> 01:14:09,830
你不惩罚我?
You're not punishing me?

666
01:14:10,000 --> 01:14:13,420
这有什么意义
What could possibly be the point?

667
01:14:26,190 --> 01:14:28,780
我来给你举个健康情绪的例子
Well, let me give you an example of emotional wellness.

668
01:14:28,940 --> 01:14:34,030
你知道有时说不是有多困难
You know how difficult it is sometimes to say no. And how good it feels...

669
01:14:34,200 --> 01:14:38,710
而当你找到勇气说出口时 感觉会会很棒 这是为什么呢
When you finally find the courage to say it anyway. Why is that?

670
01:14:39,430 --> 01:14:41,420
你有空吗
Do you have a moment?

671
01:14:44,590 --> 01:14:46,260
怎么了
Hoi, wat is is?

672
01:14:46,420 --> 01:14:48,930
我们刚接到医院电话
We just got a call from the hospital.

673
01:14:49,100 --> 01:14:54,140
恐怕康纳的母亲快不行了 他们想要他过去
I am afraid that Conor's mother is not going to make it. They want him to come there.

674
01:15:23,290 --> 01:15:25,530
你不一起吗
Aren't you coming?

675
01:15:26,590 --> 01:15:28,760
我就待在这
I'll be right here.

676
01:16:02,100 --> 01:16:04,710
你的手怎么了
What did you do to your hands?

677
01:16:10,710 --> 01:16:13,540
是要谈话 对吗
It's the talk isn't it?

678
01:16:13,710 --> 01:16:16,920
最近每个人都想谈话
Everybody wants to have a talk lately.

679
01:16:20,850 --> 01:16:22,760
康
Con...

680
01:16:22,930 --> 01:16:25,940
看着我
Look at me.

681
01:16:29,460 --> 01:16:32,510
今早我跟医生谈过话
I spoke to the doctor this morning.

682
01:16:38,560 --> 01:16:41,740
新的治疗方式没作用
The new treatment it's... it's not working.

683
01:16:42,750 --> 01:16:45,670
紫杉树的那个?
The one from the yew tree?

684
01:16:48,400 --> 01:16:49,650
是的
Yeah.

685
01:16:50,920 --> 01:16:53,120
怎么会没作用
How can it not be working?

686
01:16:53,180 --> 01:16:57,400
一切都发生太快 超出了他们的预想
Things just happen fast. Faster than they thought.

687
01:16:57,560 --> 01:17:00,820
- 怎么会没作用呢 - 不知道
- How can it not be working? - I don't know.

688
01:17:00,980 --> 01:17:03,110
它必须要有作用
It has to.

689
01:17:08,450 --> 01:17:12,620
那现在怎么说 下一步怎么治疗
So what happens now? What's going to be the next treatment?

690
01:17:18,380 --> 01:17:20,880
我很抱歉
I'm so sorry.

691
01:17:22,360 --> 01:17:27,600
我一生中从没这么抱歉过
I've never been more sorry about anything in my life.

692
01:17:38,000 --> 01:17:40,390
你生气的话 也没事 康
It's okay that you're angry, Con.

693
01:17:41,620 --> 01:17:43,480
真的
It really is.

694
01:17:44,880 --> 01:17:48,850
我也很气自己告诉你真相
I'm pretty angry too, to tell you the truth.

695
01:17:50,480 --> 01:17:52,430
但是 康纳...
But Con...

696
01:17:57,170 --> 01:17:59,540
康纳 你在听吗
Con, are you listening?

697
01:18:02,860 --> 01:18:05,050
有一天...
One day...

698
01:18:06,490 --> 01:18:10,700
如果你回想这件事 为自己的生气而感到难过
if you look back and you feel bad for being so angry...

699
01:18:10,700 --> 01:18:16,560
你甚至可以向我倾诉 但你必须清楚 这没关系
you couldn't even speak to me, you have to know that was okay...

700
01:18:22,970 --> 01:18:25,810
我就知道你会难过
That I knew.

701
01:18:28,260 --> 01:18:34,570
因为你要对我说的 不用你说出口 我就已经知道了
Because I know everything you need to tell me without you having to say it out loud.

702
01:18:38,990 --> 01:18:42,160
如果你要摔东西
And if you need to break things...

703
01:18:43,960 --> 01:18:46,850
那就去摔吧
By God you break them.

704
01:18:47,380 --> 01:18:50,360
使劲摔
Break them good and hard.

705
01:18:50,370 --> 01:18:53,760
我会伴你左右 康
And I'll be right there, Con.

706
01:19:04,900 --> 01:19:08,140
我希望我能有100年
I wish I had a hundred years.

707
01:19:13,170 --> 01:19:17,070
能照顾你的100年
A hundred years I could give to you.

